node.text:
The harder the battle, the sweeter the victory 👑 

For the @pho3nixife Sub8 Project, I will face many battles.
The battle with history,
The battle with my limits,
And the battle with my rival - @nicolaspirigofficial 

This is going to be a whole new push on what’s possible but I am ready to take on the battle and prove what I can do 🥇

#DefyTheImpossible  #Pho3nix  #Sub7Sub8  #Triathlon 
🎬 @mana.studios  @orbitalstud.io |

node.text:
A short film we made during my visit to @cube.bikes , talking about my experiences as an athlete and expectations of the year ahead ⭐️ 
#sportsmotivation #cubebikes #timeforachange #2021goals #wednesdaymotivation #humpday #triathlete #ironmantraining #newyearnewbike #readytorace #teamcharlesbarclay

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lucy Charles-Barclay in Club La Santa Lanzarote with @redbull, @polarglobal, @redbulluk, @clublasanta, @tiy_products, @therabody, @live.momentous, @hollycharlesphotography_, and @cjskinhealth. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Running towards the end of week two here @clublasanta 🏃🏼‍♀️👏🏻☀️ 
Some stats from my run today:
⏰: 1hr 56mins
⛰: 313m climbed
🐶: 7 dogs spotted 
🌡: 34 degrees
🐐: 1 goat spotted 
🥤: 1 litre consumed 
💦: a whole lotta sweat 😅 
📸: @hollycharlesphotography_ 
#BloodSweatandData #lanzarote #clublasanta #running #runlikeagirl #GivesYouWings #Spottheknot #girlpower #strongwomen #livetoinspire #trichicks #WeAreAmplified #knowledgeisprogress #triathlontraining #TeamCharlesBarclay

node.text:
It’s #workoutwednesday and we are talking about the benefits of S&C for triathletes!

‘Variety is the spice of life but consistency is the key to success.’💫
This is the kind of stuff my mind generates whilst my brain is starved of oxygen in an underwater world😅
But I guess if you are consistent in the variety of swim, bike & run you’ll make a pretty good triathlete🙌🏻
📸: @hollycharlesphotography_
